What a weekend! I’m so blessed to be able to do what l love in front of the people l love! To my family and friends that always show up and show out for me, thank you! To my teammates and the rest of my road family, thank you! To the people in the HGI HQ, working behind the scenes, answering late text and doing everything possible to make sure my people had their tickets and a great experience, thank you! To the most amazing fans in sports, thank you! To this AMAZING little girl, thank you for sharing daddy with the world! I’ve made it from ATL to, NYC, to Istanbul, and finally to Catania Italy 🇮🇹. It’s crazy to think about all the places basketball has taken me… It’s really the most beautiful love/hate relationship in existence. Dunk it like you hate it, handle it like you love it and there is where you find balance. A lot of you all may see me pop across your timeline and say “Dang, Moose is still out there?” Most likely wandering if I’ve still got it. The young gunners call me OG now. 13 years of traveling the globe and entertaining the masses is a blessing. Especially after the pandemic rocked our worlds. To everyone that has ever hit that like button or reposted my videos, to those that have always supported me and my career, I humbly and graciously thank and love you all! Note back to that question… “Does Moose still got it…?” Members know. They know! 🎥JTG Thanks @speedyartis3 for continuing to let me disrespect your passes! I can’t believe I’m the girl dad of this amazing, compassionate, charismatic, fun loving, intelligent, beautiful SEVEN year old!! I’m flying to Mexico on my baby’s special day and won’t even be at her birthday party, but she is the reason I’ll never give up. Sometimes she tries my patience, but mostly enhances my resolve. This is my “why”! My Butter Muffin, Chunk-a-reena, Snookah Wookah, pumpkin! My princess, Lexi💕🥰🥹🥹🥹 Please join me in wishing her a happy 7th birthday!!💗💗💗💗💗💗💗 #birthdaygirl #birthdaybaby#girldad #princesstingz

I really have to take a moment to thank the Most High for putting me in the care of real heroes! I got sick for a few days while on tour here in Mexico and the amazing staff @hospital.moscati and Dr. @_patriciapaola_ and @fittbritt23 nursed me back to health. I am forever grateful and glad to feel like myself again🙏🏾💚🤍❤️🇲🇽. *****

¡Realmente tengo que tomarme un momento para agradecer al Altísimo por ponerme al cuidado de verdaderos héroes! Me enfermé por unos días mientras estaba de gira aquí en México y el increíble personal @hospital.moscati y la Dra. @_patriciapaola_ y @fittbritt23 me cuidaron hasta que recuperé la salud. Estaré eternamente agradecida y feliz de volver a sentirme yo misma 🙏🏾💚🤍❤️🇲🇽
